Subject: [PATCH 15/23] Improve agent summarizer tool (#5719)

* rewrite agent summarizer to chunk by context window and drop langchain

* pass aibitat into summarizer for introspection and tool approval

* drop unused caller param from summarizer introspect

* minor nits

